cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper deals with machine translation using neural networks, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which are covered under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper involves information retrieval from multilingual articles, which is covered under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with the problem of low-resource languages, which is covered under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
